name: teamlastmatches
description:
This is a sub-function API for tool esportapi.
Tool description: ESportApi offers eSports results for League of Legends, Dota 2, Counter-Strike providing also eSports standings and tournament live scores.
For increased rates and more sports, please look at: https://rapidapi.com/fluis.lacasse/api/allsportsapi2/
API description: Get the last matches for a specific E-Sports team by providing the team ID and the page number.

page.description: The page number (starting from 0) of the last matches you want to retrieve.

is_id.description: The ID of the cricket team for which you want to retrieve the last matches.
